{"id":"koenigsegg","name_cn":"柯尼塞格","name_en":"Koenigsegg","country":"瑞典","region":"europe","founded_year":1994,"logo":"/logos/koenigsegg.svg","intro":"柯尼塞格是瑞典超级跑车制造商，由Christian von Koenigsegg创立。品牌以突破性的工程创新和极致性能闻名，多次刷新量产车速度记录。","history":[{"year":1994,"event":"Christian von Koenigsegg在瑞典创立公司"},{"year":2002,"event":"CC8S正式交付，成为品牌首款量产车"},{"year":2014,"event":"One:1发布，功率重量比达1:1"},{"year":2019,"event":"Jesko发布，搭载1600马力双涡轮V8"},{"year":2022,"event":"Gemera四座超跑发布"}],"official_site":"https://www.koenigsegg.com","sources":[]}